volunteer_experiences.description:
- Providing leadership to 11 coordinators in 5 different Brazilian states;
- More than 1.6k members;
- Spreading the QA culture through discussions, learning and sharing activities;
- Training new coordinators and mentoring them on how to organize and run the event;
- Extending the event to other locations;
- Finding companies willing to receive the event;
 - Managing social platforms;
- The event is run monthly in 5 Brazilian states (São Paulo, Rio de Janeiro, Santa Catarina, Amazonas and Bahia)
- Read the garoaQA Manifesto at https://garoaqa.github.io/

https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/garoaqa/
